# Nextflow runtime + caches
.nextflow*
work/
work_*/
work-*/
**/.command.*
**/.commandbegin
**/.commandlog
**/.commandout
**/.commanderr
**/.exitcode
**/trace*.txt
**/timeline*.html
**/report*.html
**/dag*.html
**/dag*.svg

# Benchmark outputs (large / regenerated)
**/results*/
**/logs*/
**/*.out
**/*.err

# Large sequencing/alignment files
**/*.sam
**/*.bam
**/*.fastq
**/*.fastq.gz
**/*.fq
**/*.fq.gz

# Tool build artifacts / indexes
**/columba_index/
**/columba_build/
**/quik/build/
**/*.brt
**/*.bwt
**/*.cct
**/*.fsid
**/*.meta
**/*.pos
**/*.rev.brt
**/*.sa.*
**/*.sna
**/*.txt.bin
**/*.headerSN.bin

# Python artifacts
__pycache__/
*.pyc
